[ctns_make id='gen_linear_func_vertical_line']

  [ctns_front style='']
Vertical Line
  [/ctns_front]  

  [ctns_back style='width:80%;font-size:90%;']
If $$x$$ is a constant, then the graph of the linear function is a <strong>vertical line</strong>; and, the slope of this line is <em>infinite</em>.
  [/ctns_back]  

[/ctns_make]
